@startuml

left to right direction

actor PriceComparison as comparison_engine

rectangle "FIPE Lookup System" {
  comparison_engine --> (Lookup FIPE Price)

  (Lookup FIPE Price) --> (Check Cache)
  (Check Cache) --> (Cache Hit?)

  (Cache Hit?) --> (Return Cached Price)
  (Cache Hit?) --> (Normalize Vehicle Data)

  (Normalize Vehicle Data) --> (Query FIPE API)
  (Query FIPE API) --> (Parse Response)
  (Parse Response) --> (Cache Result)
  (Cache Result) --> (Return Price)

  (Query FIPE API) ..> (Handle Fuzzy Matching) : <<include>>
  (Query FIPE API) ..> (Handle API Timeout) : <<extend>>
  (Query FIPE API) ..> (Handle Rate Limiting) : <<extend>>

  (Normalize Vehicle Data) ..> (Normalize Brand) : <<include>>
  (Normalize Vehicle Data) ..> (Normalize Model) : <<include>>

  (Handle API Timeout) --> (Retry with Backoff)
  (Handle Rate Limiting) --> (Exponential Backoff)
  (Exponential Backoff) --> (Resume Query)
}

note right of (Check Cache)
  Redis or in-memory cache
  24-hour TTL
end note

note right of (Normalize Vehicle Data)
  Handle abbreviations:
  - VW → Volkswagen
  - Gol 1.0 → Gol
end note

note right of (Handle Fuzzy Matching)
  Fuzzy string distance
  for brand/model variations
end note

@enduml
